         <h2>
          <a href="//alumni.brandeis.edu/news-publications/news-archive/giving-tuesday-2018-results.html">
           Supporters come together as “One for Brandeis” on Giving Tuesday
          </a>
         </h2>
         <p>
          On November 27, 2018, 1,597 donors gave gifts totaling $438,449 for scholarships, faculty support and other university priorities, setting a single-day university record.
         </p>
         <div class="more">
          <a href="//alumni.brandeis.edu/news-publications/news-archive/giving-tuesday-2018-results.html">
