       <div class="slide">
        <a href="//alumni.brandeis.edu/news-publications/news-archive/susan-eisenberg-jay.html">
         <img alt="Dr. Susan Eisenberg Jay ’71" src="//alumni.brandeis.edu/images/news/susan-jay.jpg"/>
        </a>
        <div class="info">
         <div class="category">
         </div>
         <h2>
          <a href="//alumni.brandeis.edu/news-publications/news-archive/susan-eisenberg-jay.html">
           Brandeis is in the DNA of dedicated alumna
          </a>
         </h2>
         <p>
          Whether serving as a leader in the Brandeis National Committee or joining the Sachar Legacy Society by including the university in her estate plans, Dr. Susan Eisenberg Jay ’71 has been deeply committed to supporting Brandeis for decades.
         </p>
         <div class="more">
          <a href="//alumni.brandeis.edu/news-publications/news-archive/susan-eisenberg-jay.html">
           <span class="text">
            more
           </span>
          </a>
          <span class="arrow">
           »
          </span>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
     <p class="intro">
      Brandeis relies on the support of alumni, parents and friends to educate the best students, maintain a world-class faculty, provide state-of-the-art classroom and laboratory facilities, and offer dynamic extracurricular programming.
     </p>
     <div class="callout">
      <h2>
       Brandeis Fund
      </h2>
      <div class="wysiwyg">
       <iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="360" mozallowfullscreen="" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/196337704" webkitallowfullscreen="" width="640">
       </iframe>
       <p>
        <span>
         The Brandeis Fund helps students find their passions – whether in the
        </span>
        <a href="http://giving.brandeis.edu/videos/bfund1.html">
         library
        </a>
        <span>
         , in a
        </span>
        <a href="http://giving.brandeis.edu/videos/bfund2.html">
         lab
        </a>
        <span>
         , on a stage, in a classroom, on an athletic field or in an art studio.
        </span>
       </p>
      </div>
